Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.89,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get! Cherry pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.48,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}RAN-RAN Welcome party
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.09,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look up! Sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:51.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.16,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The presence... of asteroids!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:55.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As they confoundedly collide and melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.54,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sing loudly! Like a Sirenger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.70,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:03.15,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be the one with the last laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:10.05,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I'm wearing a sailor uniform {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}And that's that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.31,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though it's only Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.80,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm feeling horrible. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:22.85,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The summer clothes are so much better! {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}Oh, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.96,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's getting close to 3 picts. Yet, I'm still hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:30.00,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try your best! Get your spirits up! My Darlin' darlin' PLEASE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:02.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Class 3-B?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Kuroi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:05.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:32.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for treating us today, Cousin Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:34.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:37.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:38.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:41.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel happy when the egg tastes good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The price of gas went up two yen since yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:49.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should've filled up the tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.11,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Why is it that people who spend generously...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.94,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}...care so much about a one yen difference in the price of gasoline?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That book I lent you a while ago is\N apparently getting turned into a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:01:59.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be buying it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:01.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so behind, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:05.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I reserved the limited edition as soon as it was announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:08.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I even bought the DVD box set for\N the anime and other related goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:10.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more hooked than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty common for people to become bigger\N fans than the people who recommend stuff to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Cousin Yui chose her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:17.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to someone else's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:18.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I lent her a racing manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary how much energy people put into their hobbies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:27.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday was the third win in a row, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:30.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the start of a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.98,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If they keep on winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:33.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:35.11,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...the playoffs and Japan Series aren't out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably pro baseball, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.24,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All the way to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:37.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher enjoys it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.80,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Besides, baseball's all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:38.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:41.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous poet, Shiki Masaoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...apparently loved baseball a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He played catcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...until he was too ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And he took his childhood name, Noboru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wrote it using the characters for baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and pronounced it Noball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:55.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:59.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The winners of the Major League\N are called the world champions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about the Japan Series reminded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when it only includes American teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:11.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they should beat our team before\N they call themselves world champions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's awfully pumped up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:17.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:18.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:18.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:19.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me how to do these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:28.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You asking a question about schoolwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:32.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of these problems are quite difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:36.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cause they're from an arcade quiz game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with academic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:41.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And put more effort into your studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're applying for college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be like this here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they call me a sage over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:54.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...just enroll in that whatever academy of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I didn't get enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long were you up playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:01.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you're always in bed by eleven, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking when I looked at Miyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you haven't grown much considering how much you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:14.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Big Sister said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sensitive about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for calling so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Iwasaki residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,May I speak with Minami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She already went to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:32.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did she always sleep this early?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.44,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Pittan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.23,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,La-la moji pittan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're having fun singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we'll make do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:58.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let my father know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After the ground-breaking ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, there you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:12.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm underage, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:15.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:17.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:17.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:18.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't see you gesturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a force of habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:27.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:32.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm on the phone, I have to concentrate, so I stop gaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:35.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but then my empty hand starts feeling lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:38.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:43.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I was using a roller to get rid of dust the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll! Roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like that can get pretty addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:50.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like random doodling or menial chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:56.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get off the phone, that stuff gets old really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:59.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda depressing when only the area around you is clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could just finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My passion fades with the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just leave it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's kinda stinky, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:14.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:14.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,**cky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:15.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Po***!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:17.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...back in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:21.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:23.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of things we did when we were little...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I used to stir my yogurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and go, "Bread factory!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bread factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:39.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bread factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be embarrassed. Just 'fess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About that game I lent you back during first semester...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else wants to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:47.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:48.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it for the squirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:51.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lent a bunch to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I should get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you sure are amazing, Hiiragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:01.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, I found these games and\N didn't remember who I borrowed them from...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:03.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are some I lent to other people that I've forgotten about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:09.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be a Law of Equal Lending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a universal principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:15.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:21.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:22.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:24.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:25.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what's u—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:30.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Potemkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:31.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:33.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:34.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:35.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:36.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was something super important...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget it if it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:48.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking at the numbers for the Autumn Jumbo Lottery...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but mine were all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's not so easy to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent in a bunch of postcards...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I didn't win any prizes from the drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:00.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you never win...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:05.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you start to wonder if the vendors or\N editors are running some kind of scam, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:06.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be so suspicious of other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:11.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No good...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:13.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna call it a night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll go to the bathroom first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They tell me that I talk to myself too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:24.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was really sleepy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:34.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so why am I so awake after that weird joke?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really can't do this at night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not feeling it tonight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should get to bed while I'm dozing off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:47.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was really sleepy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:55.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so why am I so awake just 'cause it's cold under the covers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's useless...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's warm tonight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I can fall asleep quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My legs are really hot for some reason...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:08.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't fall asleep!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does this only happen to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:19.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the season for baked sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:21.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, so don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll gain weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You still said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I've made eye contact with the guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'd be rude not to buy one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:34.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Will she buy one?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"My feelings will be hurt if she doesn't."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:39.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make eye contact at Comiket...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's really hard to put a book back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:48.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care when other people have\N no idea what you're talking about, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about when you're hanging around a circle's booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you pick up a book in front of a sales rep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you feel pretty bad if you leave without buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still put it back, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:04.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been an increase in the number\N of light novels being adapted to anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The novel I lent you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...has already had three anime adaptations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there should be a new volume coming out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've watched the anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I haven't read the novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much text makes me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:17.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That again, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:21.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the games you always play have a lot more text?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They should, but it's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd really help if they released them in a visual novel format.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:28.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:31.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When are they doing the fourth season of the anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that some kind of reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:52.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The lid always ends up crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, some people are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's clumsiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:00.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:04.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You share some cute flaws with Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:08.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are amazing, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:15.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I used my usual strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't open the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:35.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we just tear it along the notches?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:35.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open it, so hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:46.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just tear along the notches or use scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:48.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that would hurt my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or make me feel like a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister, is it a mosquito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:02.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:05.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get annoyed when you know something's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you haven't been bitten yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you know it's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you must take it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:12.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the instinct of a hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:16.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If a guy in the same year professed his love for Yu-chan or me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:24.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't that guy be a lolicon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the same class year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so technically, they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:33.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But in this case, it feels like appearance holds more weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, if...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you were a 30-year-old who\N looked like someone in grade school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you could say the guy likes older women...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:43.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a complicated issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to come up with a strict definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:50.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami would have just ended it with, "Who cares?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell in love with Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:57.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you dote on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...which means you're a lolicon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:12:59.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:00.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not entirely accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:03.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not limited to little girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also like normal girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should say that I'm {\i1}also{\i0} a lolicon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it basically depends on the character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:12.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you fail as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:13.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:16.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you're always so clingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:19.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you still be like that if I were a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:22.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:26.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad I'm a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:30.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the bath should be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You go first, Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:33.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:36.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He chased her away 'cause he was looking bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was short...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and your childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she like a character out of a gal game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was adorable since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:53.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why you fell for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but why did she marry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I once said, "You wouldn't accept me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I ended up as a gal game lover!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she just said yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that coercion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't the only reason, obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:14.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was really happy when you were born...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:14.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this mole make her look like you, Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She has your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can definitely tell she's our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:26.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I hope she doesn't grow up like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she doesn't inherit my height...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...or your personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:35.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you suddenly mention her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:39.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lonely without Mom around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:48.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:51.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You create as much excitement as two people would.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:53.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yu-chan's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kanata...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Konata's grown up to be a good girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:01.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though she's not as normal as you wanted...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:04.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:10.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't die before I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:13.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I have no intention of doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:13.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata died young...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she said she was happy and smiled at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard on those left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I want to be like that at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So how do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:28.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Death by over-arousal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:33.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely going to have a bizarre death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:38.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought a digital camera for work today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:58.91,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I haven't been back in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:02.96,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I wonder what...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:02.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! I'm in the middle of a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:04.55,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...they're doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:05.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:06.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And Dad, you're way too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so heartless, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:21.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking photos to commemorate this new camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you buy this for work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.57,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.57,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sou-kun hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:25.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One more picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:26.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.44,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's right, you never did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.68,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...pay much attention to what other people wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:31.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:32.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:38.43,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You really haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:43.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel more and more like Kanata when I hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't just blurt out risqué statements!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see what Mom had to put up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.09,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.55,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Your dad may be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.49,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...but don't turn into a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:59.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:02.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me that one game once you clear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That one's surprisingly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.57,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:10.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I made a wrong choice somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.49,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They play games together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.36,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...so it looks like they're getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make it to the H-scene for the character I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:14.45,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.89,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What are you letting your daughter play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.08,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.75,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:22.35,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Aren't you teaching her the wrong things, Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Mom choose you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:30.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause you're just an old, perverted, lolicon otaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:32.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People usually don't go for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't go easy on your old man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.83,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.93,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata had really good intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.77,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You were always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.42,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Always making me almost forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.69,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...why I chose to spend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I failed as a human being...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.53,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...my life with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:54.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was one thing I was absolutely sure about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:00.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One thing you were absolutely sure about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the one who loved Kanata most in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.39,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:20.10,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I just can't beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.72,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He accepts my good and bad parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.36,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He's willing to show both...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.78,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...his good and bad parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:09.81,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The place I feel most at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:13.57,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The place that lets me feel most at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:16.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:18.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:19.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we take another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do one with Yu-chan later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:25.20,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The fact that I can no longer be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:24.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And that would be more than one picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.89,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...hurts a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:26.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought this for your hobby, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:35.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just testing it out before I take pictures for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:35.98,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.89,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If I can live on inside them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:43.49,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...the way the two of them exist inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.60,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...I'll continue to watch over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:47.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:48.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:51.44,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}May the ones who brought me so much joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:51.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:53.86,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...be blessed with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.86,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I wonder if they'll be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:02.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:07.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a shadow back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A real ghost picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.12,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with my bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:12.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-Yu-Yu-Yu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:14.48,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:17.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:19.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.76,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:23.80,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:24.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Deleting it isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we have to burn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:29.35,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't burn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've talked with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have a different impression of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Mina-rin still seems a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:40.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:47.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.04,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Those two are really close.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:49.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You had classroom duty today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the teacher still in the faculty office?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:52.12,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}This would be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yutaka, your tie is crooked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B-Big Sister..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mustn't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:59.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm looking at my friends weird again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe it's been building up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:07.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:08.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:13.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't find them anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't find their managers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, either way, they're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:18.42,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:19.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:20.17,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rolling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:22.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bad feeling about this show from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:23.36,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:23.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:23.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually refused in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But all that politics crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:28.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Grown-up issues and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:29.25,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:30.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it's rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:31.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's rolling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:32.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:32.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:33.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:34.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:35.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:37.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that the camera's rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:37.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:38.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:13.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.81,0:23:14.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Soujirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:15.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:16.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Sou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:18.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be heading off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:22.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:24.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to leave my body yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:25.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm sure I can learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:28.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun, you're talking about manga or anime again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:29.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:31.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:32.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:33.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A Fine Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:35.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun!
